markets.title: Bloodline (with Jelly Roll) streams by May 30, 2025?
markets.rules_primary: If Bloodline (with Jelly Roll) by Alex Warren, Jelly Roll has above 13 million total streams on Spotify on May 30, 2025 at 10 AM ET, then the market resolves to Yes.
markets.rules_secondary: Total stream count will be determined using the Spotify desktop app at 10 AM ET, based on the exact number displayed at that time. Any updates or changes after 10 AM ET will NOT be considered. The following song can be found here: https://open.spotify.com/track/0qmhTHMVxnXRmT5N92wTD9?si=fc43c65974244ebe
markets.early_close_condition: This market will close and expire early if the event occurs.
